{"tid":1419913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議機場 播片播警犬打壓 文宣集中五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:22:45.000Z","uid":207614,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90826c0e0ebcfb3b113bd21b56ba5da0985450e4","tid":1419913,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"講多無謂 睇片最實際<br />\n集齊各大記者既警黑片 集中播放<br />\n<br />\n而派文宣 可以集中五大訴求<br />\n簡而精 將焦點放返落政權到<br />\n當然附隨一兩張警黑過期催淚彈冇問題<br />\n<br />\n要向全世界重申一次<br />\n我地既勇武又好 和理非又好<br />\n<br />\n目的只有五大訴求<br />\n槍口永遠對準政權 政權包括軍犬政府<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"a86479e0ce2ad5b9fb762905fff362916fba2ac5","tid":1419913,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"我推 我推 我推推推"},{"pid":"560616cea5f79127f465445ad232d0f6c1e63a28","tid":1419913,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41b934d4edf24621cfa13f7b0d8a16dce01a8f88","tid":1419913,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2feb8aa1f7097b59c685c5fb742d18d808ff75e5","tid":1419913,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:07:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1d0350dec8e5b7690e5cc5be2cc005ae3606c03","tid":1419913,"uid":285317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:08:06.000Z","msg":"張執到嘅彈殼排好<br />\n下面補一句<br />\nWe request for freedom and democracy<br />\nWe refuse China Extradition bill<br />\nBut these are what we've got<br />\n<br />\n利申：我英文差，搵啲讀英文嘅搞搞佢"},{"pid":"9ffeb842ada1b9661b9c381c86c0ef363d0cb674","tid":1419913,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:51:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e22d1d589e1d19bee652efb1856ea0b50a4bba65","tid":1419913,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"pishhhh"},{"pid":"